.SH "NAME"
sonicweb \- Small secure static file server.
.\"SKIP_SECTION"
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.B sonicweb
[\-root path]
[\-base path]
[\-port number]
[\-address address]
[\-iport number]
[\-iaddress address]
[\-telemetry {true,false}]
[\-trace-endpoint address]
[\-pprof {true,false}]
[\-log level {debug,info,warn,error}]
[\-logstyle {auto,text,json}]
.\"NODE "DESCRIPTION"
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
SonicWeb is a small static fileserver that has the web application firewall of corasa integrated.
.\"NODE "OPTIONS"
.\"DONT_SPLIT"
.SH "OPTIONS"
.TP
.I \-root path
Set the root path for served files in the filesystem. Defaults to
.BR /www
.TP
.I \-base path
Set the base path in the URLs to be that. Defaults to
.BR /
.TP
.I \-port number
Set the listen port to number. Defaults to
.BR 8080
.TP
.I \-address address
Set the listen address. Defaults to
.BR "all\ addresses".
.TP
.I \-header <header>
Add given HTTP header to responses, may be repeated
.TP
.I \-headerFile <file>
Add HTTP headers from given file to responses, may be repeated
.TP
.I \-iport number
Set the listen port for telemetry requests. Defaults to
.BR 8081
.TP
.I \-iaddress address
Set the listen address for telemetry requests. Defaults to
.BR "all\ addresses".
.TP
.I \-telemetry {true,false}
Enable or disable telemetry support. Defaults to
.BR true
.TP
.I \-trace-endpoint address
Set the endpoint for the tracing facility. Defaults to
.BR <empty>
.TP
.I \-pprof {true,false}
Enable or disable the pprof support for remote debugging. Defaults to
.BR false
.TP
.I \-log level {debug,info,warn,error}
Set the log level. Defaults to
.BR info
.TP
.I \-logstyle {auto,text,json}
Set the logging style. Defaults to
.BR auto
.TP
.I \-help
Print help about possible arguments and exit.
.TP
.I \-version
Print the version information and exit.
